{"tid":2142627,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"LOTR已經有BNO成功申請個案","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T15:54:10.000Z","uid":285195,"like":118,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"07babb51397df51751ecd554d1b8c3d823a57346","tid":2142627,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:59:15.000Z","msg":"利申：樓豬本人未申請過LOTR，下文內容純粹只係整合自網友提供之內容<br />\n<br />\n拍片者講述自己到達英國申請LOTR狀況，整個過程用咗十零分鐘左右。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TvYnTYoXLZY&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTvYnTYoXLZY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26app%3Ddesktop&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOujOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=6d7caf77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TvYnTYoXLZY&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;app=desktop</a><br />\nBNO成功入境英國！細節逐個講！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxpE1TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxpE1TY.jpg&h=a0e5fa66&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLOTR印：<br />\n&quot;No recourse to public funds&quot;，但沒有&quot;No work&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3VHZFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3VHZFJ.jpg&h=61012227&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一般BNO以旅客身份入境英國印：<br />\n&quot;No work or recourse to public funds&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKftaNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKftaNa.jpg&h=ea4f1d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YPQ8yU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YPQ8yU.jpg&h=371c944b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓豬補充：<br />\n買單程機票，被香港入境處及機場地勤職員諸多阻欄風險，比申請LOTR被英國邊防人員刁難風險高出好多好多！唔好忘記，原本已經上咗飛機但最後被召回既不幸手足都係買單程機票的。<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1) 如果擔心來回機票去到英國申請LOTR被英國邊防人員問長問短，可以照樣買來回機票去英國，但到達後再離開英國國境，然後又再以單程機票返番英國，然後先再申請LOTR。<br />\n2) 先買來回機票去其它中轉站國家，然後再以單程機票去英國申請LOTR。但唔好途經啲仆街奶共國家如東亞(新加坡除外)，中東等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦聽聞英國唔同機場邊防人員批出LOTR手鬆程度都有唔同，A機場失敗唔代表B機場都必定會失敗。亂世時間資訊混亂係正常現象。<br />\n<br />\n同埋收到消息，話香港機場近幾日已經停晒E道，入境處全人手check出境證件。原因自己諗吧！<br />\n<br />\n最後俾少少個人忠告。遲走危險因素：<br />\n<br />\n1) 因肺炎各國再次封關。即使英國不可以阻止BNO holders入境，但不能取道其它封關國家轉機。<br />\n<br />\n2) 肺炎令航班大減甚至取消。<br />\n<br />\n3) 中共封鎖邊境禁止有中國籍人士出境。呢樣嘢二戰時希特拉已經做過，刁種都一樣絕對做得出。<br />\n<br />\n4) 中印開戰，印度封鎖領空，航線改道引致航班大混亂。就算目前解放軍已經撤兵，但會唔會死灰復燃真係得刁種自己先至知。<br />\n<br />\n5) 南海開戰，香港機場咩航班都收皮。<br />\n<br />\n6）美國已經取消香港特殊待遇，將特區護照當成中國護照同等處理。其它西方國家好快會陸續跟隊，取消特區護照免簽證待遇。<br />\n<br />\n7）美國取消聯繫匯率，港元大跌，但機票以美元計價，結果機票價格大升。<br />\n<br />\n8) 早走更加係為大局著想，免得去到最危急最多人需要走既時候，先至同一時間冚世界一齊衝出嚟搶奪機位。呢個直頭係關乎公共資源利益問題。"},{"pid":"e161b12af47e3dd80e6f4ce2c9061d0892513367","tid":2142627,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6125af40ec8fe17e897798c4e2740f3cc0d1a9","tid":2142627,"uid":2954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7731a987dc6b495e2444028f34c682a14eceec9a","tid":2142627,"uid":107419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"恭喜。<br />\n其他手足加油。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5288f712581e13ce5da8351d9cb13c6354e7aa","tid":2142627,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"堅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adb9c070154088e87de0259a749642f98349dbd","tid":2142627,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"fb仲有班人叫人唔好用LOTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班友真係累撚人死"},{"pid":"84da79b8b043617567beb83d7501bcfc386bed5e","tid":2142627,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c04f8a61081822450dd6bb4b30c2fb29fa74eea1","tid":2142627,"uid":243366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"咁姐係應唔應該買單程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6665ae5d99eb9a8ab0374f1f731d67d09c7b68a","tid":2142627,"uid":109075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恭喜巴打成功甩難"},{"pid":"32481b4e25c878476156b325a27176ed77071587","tid":2142627,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"買單程機票，被香港入境處及機場地勤職員諸多阻欄風險，比申請LOTR被英國邊防人員刁難風險高出好多好多！唔好忘記，原本已經上咗飛機但最後被召回既不幸手足都係買單程機票的。<br />\n樓主講呢個<br />\n<br />\n但係人哋NOTES 唔可以買來回 姐係點啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055b5f1379da083032ef1e4d3c9930424d3f96a3","tid":2142627,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議：<br />\n1) 如果擔心來回機票去到英國申請LOTR被英國邊防人員問長問短，可以照樣買來回機票去英國，但到達後再離開英國國境，然後又再以單程機票返番英國，然後先再申請LOTR。</blockquote><br />\n咁早會累死人<br />\n英國好撚麻煩, 出完境再入有排查"},{"pid":"41d3a5f5ce584083e55ce916a796911e0584bffb","tid":2142627,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200806/MWL62CZ5SFG6JDO7KQZIIFYVJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200806%2FMWL62CZ5SFG6JDO7KQZIIFYVJ4%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOujOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=4317d647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200806%2FMWL62CZ5SFG6JDO7KQZIIFYVJ4%2F&h=8dfcd819\" data-auto-li